title: A treatise of the nobilitie and excellencye of vvoman kynde, translated out of Latine into englysshe by Dauid Clapam
author: Agrippa von Nettesheim, Heinrich Cornelius, 1486?-1535.
publisher: In ædibus Thomæ Bertheleti typis impress.],
notes: Translation of: Declamatio de nobilitate et praecellentia foeminei sexus.
Composed in compliment to Margaret of Austria.
Place of publication and printer's name from colophon.
The last leaf bears a printer's mark.
Running title reads: Nobilitie of vvoman kynde.
Reproduction of the original in the Bodleian Library.
